== Installation ==

=== USE flags ===

{{USEflag|package=net-ftp/proftpd}}

=== Emerge ===

{{Emerge|net-ftp/proftpd}}

== Configuration ==

=== Anonymous read access ===

Anonymous read only access requires <code>-acl</code> USE flag set.  Permissions on {{Path|/home/ftp}} require {{c|chmod 555}} ran on the directory.

{{FileBox|filename=/etc/proftpd/proftpd.conf|1=
<Anonymous /home/ftp>
}}

== Service ==

=== OpenRC ===

To start ProFTPD on boot:

{{RootCmd|rc-update add proftpd default}}

To start ProFTPD now:

{{RootCmd|rc-service proftpd start}}

=== systemd ===

To start ProFTPD on boot:

{{RootCmd|systemctl enable proftpd}}

To start ProFTPD now:

{{RootCmd|systemctl start proftpd}}

